source.name: Census 2000 Summary File 3 (SF3)
source.description: Provides detailed sample information from Census 2000.  It consists of 813 tables of social, economic and housing characteristics compiled from a sample of approximately 19 million housing units (about 1 in 6 households) that received the Census 2000 long-form questionnaire. Fifty-one tables are repeated for nine major race and Hispanic or Latino groups.
